=====Usage notes=====
* This usage, once widespread in the UK, is now confined to the US (or perhaps parts thereof). The use of ''loan'' as a verb is occasionally disapproved of, especially when the object being lent is something other than money; as a consequence, {{m|en|lend}} is often preferred.

